description: Many #ENVtuber gamer gals ✨ | Plural! Trans!! ASD+ADHD!!! | Partnered w/ @twitch @discordapp | Powered by @AVerMedia @HermanMiller @Audeze | Art: #SystemOfStars
tweet:
That being said, my new insurance kicks in soon. I'll be seeing a new therapist, hopefully in person, and working towards proper answers as to what's going on inside my head and why...

For now, just know that I'm still three girls in a trenchcoat, just relabeled. We're plural. https://t.co/vvXOnZ1wlg

name: Star System ✨ Plural ENVTubers
description: Many #ENVtuber gamer gals ✨ | Plural! Trans!! ASD+ADHD!!! | Partnered w/ @twitch @discordapp | Powered by @AVerMedia @HermanMiller @Audeze | Art: #SystemOfStars
tweet:
That doesn't mean I'm not going to seek answers. In fact, I'm gonna do more than that.

I'm in a unique position where I've already been creating content for a bit now with a focus on mental health, so I'm going to use my experiences to help educate others. We can learn together!

name: Star System ✨ Plural ENVTubers
description: Many #ENVtuber gamer gals ✨ | Plural! Trans!! ASD+ADHD!!! | Partnered w/ @twitch @discordapp | Powered by @AVerMedia @HermanMiller @Audeze | Art: #SystemOfStars
tweet:
Now look, I'm not a therapist, and I'm still not going to label myself with either DID or OSDD of any variety, BUT

Diagnoses like these take a VERY long time to get, so self diagnosing is absolutely valid if you decide to.

The label is irrelevant to me though, so I won't yet.

name: Star System ✨ Plural ENVTubers
description: Many #ENVtuber gamer gals ✨ | Plural! Trans!! ASD+ADHD!!! | Partnered w/ @twitch @discordapp | Powered by @AVerMedia @HermanMiller @Audeze | Art: #SystemOfStars
tweet:
Anyway, later on, it happened again with the other alter, and now we're all able to communicate together, and switch (though it isn't simply being able to whenever we want, fff) 

At this point, I'm not just 'me' anymore. We're us, and that's undeniable - for better or for worse.

name: Star System ✨ Plural ENVTubers
description: Many #ENVtuber gamer gals ✨ | Plural! Trans!! ASD+ADHD!!! | Partnered w/ @twitch @discordapp | Powered by @AVerMedia @HermanMiller @Audeze | Art: #SystemOfStars
tweet:
But I'm still scared of what people will think of me - what'll happen with my career in streaming, or if my mental health will worsen... 

I'm still terrified, but normality isn't an option... I'm broken in my own unique way. But there's nothing wrong with being broken...

name: Star System ✨ Plural ENVTubers
description: Many #ENVtuber gamer gals ✨ | Plural! Trans!! ASD+ADHD!!! | Partnered w/ @twitch @discordapp | Powered by @AVerMedia @HermanMiller @Audeze | Art: #SystemOfStars
tweet:
But things progressed, and one day after a particularly odd day of blurred identity (not being sure of who you are) I was able to communicate with one of my alters internally (and even switch, I think? on our own!) 

As crazy as this sounds, I felt... validated.

name: Star System ✨ Plural ENVTubers
description: Many #ENVtuber gamer gals ✨ | Plural! Trans!! ASD+ADHD!!! | Partnered w/ @twitch @discordapp | Powered by @AVerMedia @HermanMiller @Audeze | Art: #SystemOfStars
tweet:
But again, switching was rare. Maybe I wasn't plural. Maybe I was lying to myself, etc... right?

Dissociative systems usually switch more often than we did, so, maybe I'm dealing with something different...

This can't be DID or OSDD, right?

name: Star System ✨ Plural ENVTubers
description: Many #ENVtuber gamer gals ✨ | Plural! Trans!! ASD+ADHD!!! | Partnered w/ @twitch @discordapp | Powered by @AVerMedia @HermanMiller @Audeze | Art: #SystemOfStars
tweet:
That was assuming I only had the one.

But then I was evicted. And then a second one came along, except, we share memories this time! Strange. 

Clearly, something is wrong.

name: Star System ✨ Plural ENVTubers
description: Many #ENVtuber gamer gals ✨ | Plural! Trans!! ASD+ADHD!!! | Partnered w/ @twitch @discordapp | Powered by @AVerMedia @HermanMiller @Audeze | Art: #SystemOfStars
tweet:
I thought I was lying to myself - maybe for attention? But what did I have to gain? 

But if this was real, why didn't it happen more often? Or why couldn't we communicate to each other internally? And most systems have tons of alters, so why do I have only one?

name: Star System ✨ Plural ENVTubers
description: Many #ENVtuber gamer gals ✨ | Plural! Trans!! ASD+ADHD!!! | Partnered w/ @twitch @discordapp | Powered by @AVerMedia @HermanMiller @Audeze | Art: #SystemOfStars
tweet:
Dissociation on its own is hard enough, but having someone else step in your place is... terrifying. I feared what was happening to me. Eventually I told stream, and y'all have helped me get a grasp of what's happening.

But I still wouldn't identify as plural. Why? Well...

name: Star System ✨ Plural ENVTubers
description: Many #ENVtuber gamer gals ✨ | Plural! Trans!! ASD+ADHD!!! | Partnered w/ @twitch @discordapp | Powered by @AVerMedia @HermanMiller @Audeze | Art: #SystemOfStars
tweet:
With frequency came intensity - in these moments, not only would I not act myself, but upon review, I'd sound different and play different. I wasn't myself, that was for sure. 

So I started leaving myself notes in my phone, and learned to communicate with myself like that.

name: Star System ✨ Plural ENVTubers
description: Many #ENVtuber gamer gals ✨ | Plural! Trans!! ASD+ADHD!!! | Partnered w/ @twitch @discordapp | Powered by @AVerMedia @HermanMiller @Audeze | Art: #SystemOfStars
tweet:
Why am I deciding to label myself plural now? Previously, I've struggled with dissociation, memory gaps, flashbacks, etc... and during dissociation, I act far different than normal.

But that was occasional. Ongoing, but occasional. But then it started to happen more frequently.

Oh, and one last thing I'll add, because I see it a bunch...

Anyone, literally ANYONE can feel like this. Depression doesn't care about your success in life, or how things are going overall... 

Don't think that someone's emotions aren't valid because "they're successful!!!"

name: Star System ✨ Plural ENVTubers
description: Many #ENVtuber gamer gals ✨ | Plural! Trans!! ASD+ADHD!!! | Partnered w/ @twitch @discordapp | Powered by @AVerMedia @HermanMiller @Audeze | Art: #SystemOfStars
tweet: That isn't to say that I still don't have suicidal thoughts sometimes... My most frequent suicidal thoughts are walking into cars, or throwing myself off of a second or third story, so I try to steer clear of situations that cause those thoughts (walking with friends helps!)

name: Star System ✨ Plural ENVTubers
description: Many #ENVtuber gamer gals ✨ | Plural! Trans!! ASD+ADHD!!! | Partnered w/ @twitch @discordapp | Powered by @AVerMedia @HermanMiller @Audeze | Art: #SystemOfStars
tweet:
As I said, I don't expect my experiences to be the be-all-end-all of self harm & suicidal experiences, and you shouldn't apply this knowledge to everyone who self harms or is suicidal - just be a supportive friend to them, kay?

And yes, I'm doing better, haven't harmed since! https://t.co/7mLhHyh1XY

name: Star System ✨ Plural ENVTubers
description: Many #ENVtuber gamer gals ✨ | Plural! Trans!! ASD+ADHD!!! | Partnered w/ @twitch @discordapp | Powered by @AVerMedia @HermanMiller @Audeze | Art: #SystemOfStars
tweet:
Things you should NOT do/say!

- saying things aren't "that" bad, minimizing their struggles, etc
- "I won't be your friend anymore if you continue"
- tease or place shame/guilt on them
- get upset if they don't want to talk about it
- tell others about their SH behind their back

name: Star System ✨ Plural ENVTubers
description: Many #ENVtuber gamer gals ✨ | Plural! Trans!! ASD+ADHD!!! | Partnered w/ @twitch @discordapp | Powered by @AVerMedia @HermanMiller @Audeze | Art: #SystemOfStars
tweet:
If its someone you do know well:

- Offer to be there for them in times of need, even if not "immediately necessary"
- Positively reinforce talking about problems 
- Its okay to check in, just try not to pry too hard - if we don't want to talk about it, please respect that

- do NOT draw attention to their scars

name: Star System ✨ Plural ENVTubers
description: Many #ENVtuber gamer gals ✨ | Plural! Trans!! ASD+ADHD!!! | Partnered w/ @twitch @discordapp | Powered by @AVerMedia @HermanMiller @Audeze | Art: #SystemOfStars

When I told her others thought she was abusive towards me, she continued yelling and raging at me, telling me to not come to her funeral

She told me to get out. I was immediately put on notice of eviction.

To start with a bad example, one day I forgot to wear my hoodie around the house, and my mother saw them.

I tried to lie, saying they were just my old scars that "reopened" which didn't work, obviously.

She tore into me for cutting myself, saying I had no reason to feel so bad.

This photo is from a few days after self harming - very visible. Of course, this leads to some struggles even after the bleeding stops.

name: Star System ✨ Plural ENVTubers
description: Many #ENVtuber gamer gals ✨ | Plural! Trans!! ASD+ADHD!!! | Partnered w/ @twitch @discordapp | Powered by @AVerMedia @HermanMiller @Audeze | Art: #SystemOfStars
tweet:
Not everyone self harms for the same reason! There's actually a lot of reasons why someone would, such as:

-low self esteem
-relationship issues
-lack of love/affection from family
-loneliness/isolation
-any kind of abuse

PLEASE understand that -NOBODY- SHs "just for attention"

name: Star System ✨ Plural ENVTubers

Let me just start off by talking about why I self harmed.

I felt responsible for a conflict between a group of my friends and how it hurt many of them, which made me feel self hatred more and more. Eventually, I stopped being able to feel anything.

That drove me to cut myself.
